Product name: 100% Natural Ayurvedic eyelash serum oil eyebrow  growth conditioner 11 ml - thicker longer healthier lashes rosemary essential oil Ayurveda
Description:
Eyelash eyebrow serum - 100% Natural- 100% chemical and preservative free.
INGREDIENTS:  Cold pressed, extra virgin Organic Castor oil (Hexane free),amla oil,Bringaraj,	Brahmi,Amla, Vitamin E oil,jojoba oil,almond oil,lavender Essential oil	Rosemary essential oil,Litsea cubeba essential oil.	
Castor oil is one of the best kept secrets in the world of natural beauty.  Taken from the bean of the Castor plant, this oil is rich in ricinoleic acid (omega-9 fatty acid), which exerts powerful therapeutic effects. It will help your eyelashes to grow thick and long, and can keep them from breaking. It can also help you grow new eyebrow hair in bare areas that might have been over-tweezed. This unique blend of carefully chosen oils will nourish and condition eyelashes and brows making it longer healthier and stronger.
DIRECTIONS:With just a swipe or two on your eyelashes every night before bedtime and again each morning. The same directions apply for your eyebrows as well.This serum is safe to use up to 3 times a day if desired and won't irritate your eyes
MY PERSONAL REVIEW:
 " 100% Natural Lubricant for the eyes"
Excellent eye make up remover & its 100% Natural. At bedtime, I apply the "roll on tube" ( I use kajal  eye liner heavily)and wipe off the kajal, now I apply a second coat to stimulate hair growth.
As a toddler I didn't have much of eyebrow hair and my aunt & mom used to apply castor oil on my eyebrows and till now it grows crazy, I need to thread them every 20 days :-(, I'm a believer " Castor oil helps hair grow :-)

Product name: Royalty Symbols - Glass Decal - Ceramic Decal - Fusible Glass Decals - Waterslide Transfer      9328783
Description:
Glass or Ceramic Decals
Silk Screen Glass and Ceramic Decals Fusible glass or ceramic decals for glass fusing or ceramic porcelain firing.
Waterslide decals are easy to use.  Once kiln fired, they are permanent and will not scratch or rub off.
Directions for use:
Waterslide decals are commercially printed and cover coated for easy application and firing.
Cut out decal, soak in lukewarm water, slide the decal off the paper onto your piece.  
Squeegee the water out and allot to dry overnight. 
Then fire (see temperatures below). 
Decals can be used on glass or ceramic, (If firing on ceramic please use a lower firing temperature).
Firing temperatures: 1050°F to 1300°F
